Valentine’s Day is the official holiday of love. From candy, to flowers, to jewelry there are so many traditions we observe on this day, but where did they all come from? Do you think you know all there is to know about Valentine’s Day?  Then test your knowledge with our yearly Valentine’s Day quiz. Whether you’re planning a romantic evening with your partner, grabbing drinks with your friends for ‘gal-entine’s day’ or not observing at all this quiz is sure to get you in a romantic mood. Good luck!  